title: Obama advances Mallows Bay sanctuary designation
text: The federal government is moving forward with a plan to create a national marine sanctuary at Mallows Bay in Charles County -- the site of the largest collection of historic shipwrecks in the nation -- President Barack Obama will announce Monday.
